    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "# Collect customer feedback with Google Drive and Asana on autopilot\n\n**Pattern:** Survey & Feedback · **Level:** Foundation · **Trigger:** Scheduled\n\n## What it does\nCollect customer feedback with Google Drive and Asana on autopilot. It runs automatically on a schedule.\n\n## Why it exists\nManual feedback is slow and error-prone; this workflow makes the process repeatable, monitored and hands-off, with failures surfaced instead of silently lost.\n\n## Main flow\nHourly Schedule → Gather from Google Drive → Roll Up KPIs → Write Executive Summary (AI) → Compose HTML Report → Send Report via Telegram → Sort Tickets Newest First → …\n\n## Use it for\n- Teams that want to survey & feedback without manual effort\n- Anyone automating feedback in customer support\n- Replacing a fragile manual process with a reliable workflow\n\n## You get\n- Scales without extra headcount\n- Standardizes the process every time\n- Saves hours of manual work each week\n\n## Before first run\nConnect credentials: Google OAuth2; OpenAI API key; Telegram bot token.\nFollow the color key: 🟦 entry · 🟪 AI · 🟫 actions · ⬜ utilities · 🟩 outputs · 🟥 error rail.\nEach node has its own doc card underneath — read those before editing.",
        "width": 480,
        "height": 900
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        -830,
        80
      ],
      "id": "a7f1cc67-8d27-ca85-da5b-3dcb489a8d98",
      "name": "📘 Workflow Overview"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 🤖 AI cluster\n\nPurple nodes form one AI unit: the root node orchestrates, sub-nodes plug in via typed ports (model / memory / tools / parser). Swap the chat model without rewiring anything else. Costs scale with tokens — keep prompts lean and cap iterations.",
        "width": 360,
        "height": 260,
        "color": 6
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
